5072</guid><pubDate>Tue, 21 Oct 2025 07:40:36 +0100</pubDate></item><item><title>&amp;ldquo;Terracotta anatomical votive; human eye.&amp;rdquo; 3rdC BC-1stC BC, Italy.</title><description>&lt;div class="npf_row"&gt;&lt;figure class="tmblr-full" data-orig-height="641" data-orig-width="792"&gt;&lt;img src="https://64.media.tumblr.com/e8ecf9b044607d68b2af2b04a3205374/e5f628eae9427be2-47/s640x960/46b455f08a3cd5818563de39680952b2f8959248.png" data-orig-height="641" data-orig-width="792" srcset="https://64.media.tumblr.com/e8ecf9b044607d68b2af2b04a3205374/e5f628eae9427be2-47/s75x75_c1/4ad52e2ac43382e5bb99a66ee24cb7b1933c63f8.png 75w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/e8ecf9b044607d68b2af2b04a3205374/e5f628eae9427be2-47/s100x200/a10be4166545509bac2034c9563ec5a241468b4b.png 100w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/e8ecf9b044607d68b2af2b04a3205374/e5f628eae9427be2-47/s250x400/6a98d332c94fe55d0622d78899f31e9c5e9c9622.png 250w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/e8ecf9b044607d68b2af2b04a3205374/e5f628eae9427be2-47/s400x600/4698315fc9d729567529a7fd4656285a6a447b34.png 400w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/e8ecf9b044607d68b2af2b04a3205374/e5f628eae9427be2-47/s500x750/eb0cc5ce94104cb8aec82798a4f7d770fa596e98.png 500w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/e8ecf9b044607d68b2af2b04a3205374/e5f628eae9427be2-47/s540x810/13628d3b4b96bf8b65df7de284b1c869a9544570.png 540w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/e8ecf9b044607d68b2af2b04a3205374/e5f628eae9427be2-47/s640x960/46b455f08a3cd5818563de39680952b2f8959248.png 640w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/e8ecf9b044607d68b2af2b04a3205374/e5f628eae9427be2-47/s1280x1920/b509efa5adf59911679cc16b74833dbe635e07c4.png 792w" sizes="(max-width: 792px) 100vw, 792px"/&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;&amp;ldquo;Terracotta anatomical votive; human eye.&amp;rdquo; 3rdC BC-1stC BC, Italy.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://www.britishmuseum.org/collection/object/G_1878-1019-312"&gt;British Museum&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description><link>https://stml.tumblr.com/post/797996451438395392</link><g